  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a heavy-bottomed pan over medium heat.",
    "Add mustard seeds, cumin seeds, and dried chilies, letting them sizzle for 30 seconds.",
    "Add diced onion, minced garlic, and grated ginger; sauté until onion turns translucent.",
    "Stir in tomato puree and cook for 2 minutes, letting flavors meld.",
    "Add cooked black beans and coconut milk; bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Season with salt, adjust consistency with a splash of water if needed, and let simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Finish by swirling in chopped cilantro and squeezing fresh lemon juice.",
    "Serve hot with steamed idli, plated in a clay tajine for an aromatic presentation."
